io.permazen

Interface StorageIdGenerator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultStorageIdGenerator

    public interface StorageIdGenerator
    Used to auto-generate storage ID's for Java model classes, fields, and composite indexes when not specified explicitly in the corresponding @PermazenType, @JField, etc., annotations.
    See Also:
    PermazenFactory.setStorageIdGenerator()
